      <title>My fist English Class</title>
      <link href="/2022/09/08/%E6%9C%AD%E8%AE%B0/%E6%9C%AD%E8%AE%B0/"/>
      <url>/2022/09/08/%E6%9C%AD%E8%AE%B0/%E6%9C%AD%E8%AE%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="short-talk"><a class="anchor" href="#short-talk">#</a> Short Talk</h1><p>(In fact, i want to improve my English through writing some articles in English.)</p><hr /><h3 id="my-teachers"><a class="anchor" href="#my-teachers">#</a> My teachers</h3><p>One of my teacher is a <em>Chinese</em>,while the other one is an <em>English</em>(maybe,i'm not certain,forgive me)<br />When i typing the article you see, i'm taking my foreign teacher's spoken English class.</p><hr /><h3 id="my-class"><a class="anchor" href="#my-class">#</a> My class</h3><p>The spoken English class focuses on discussion.<br />Yet my classmates are pretty shy so that few discusions happened when we were dvided into the same discuss room.</p>]]></content>
      
      
